234
00:25:08,360 --> 00:25:11,880
I can't believe someone would dare lay a hand on you.

235
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:13,960
It was not only that.

236
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:16,220
I went there to investigate the Divine-Devil War.

237
00:25:16,220 --> 00:25:18,040
I should've had my immortal memory.

238
00:25:18,040 --> 00:25:20,500
Yet, it was tampered with by someone.

239
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:28,540
