243
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:44,940
He was powerful.

244
00:25:44,940 --> 00:25:48,740
The divine arts he used are rarely seen.

245
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:53,020
It's just that I have no idea where he was from.

246
00:25:53,020 --> 00:25:58,620
Moreover, that person knew the secret method of the Devil Realm, the Puppet Spell.

247
00:25:59,280 --> 00:26:01,540
Puppet Spell?

248
00:26:08,140 --> 00:26:13,680
Could it be... a mole that the Devil Clan hid in the Heavenly Realm?

249
00:26:13,740 --> 00:26:16,020
Is it that we haven't wiped them out entirely yet?

250
00:26:16,020 --> 00:26:21,960
Since the previous Divine-Devil War, it has already been 900 years.

251
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:25,140
I'm thinking it could cause a big disaster.

252
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:33,520
Please calm down, Your Supreme Majesty.

253
00:26:33,520 --> 00:26:37,340
I fought him several times. He left me some clues.

254
00:26:37,340 --> 00:26:42,580
Since I came back, I'll find out who he is and establish the truth.

255
00:26:42,580 --> 00:26:45,700
By the way, your celestial vest was damaged,

256
00:26:45,700 --> 00:26:50,660
as a mortal going through your trials this could have been a catastrophe. It would be extremely dangerous

257
00:26:50,660 --> 00:26:55,280
if no one was there to adjust your immortal power.

258
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:58,820
Did someone help you in the Mortal Realm?

259
00:26:58,820 --> 00:27:02,180
According to the Heavenly Rules, the person who helped you will be promoted to a deity

260
00:27:02,180 --> 00:27:03,900
and be granted a thousand years of cultivation base.

261
00:27:03,900 --> 00:27:08,980
After Zhi Xi descended to the Mortal Realm, she opened this road to Heaven for you to come back.

262
00:27:08,980 --> 00:27:10,540
I'll grant her a reward.

263
00:27:10,540 --> 00:27:14,320
If there was someone else who helped you, you can also give me their names.

264
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:18,560
Right now, we haven't eliminated the mole.

265
00:27:18,560 --> 00:27:24,580
If this gets out, it could cause trouble to them instead.

266
00:27:24,580 --> 00:27:27,060
Also, this person doesn't care about the titles of the Heavenly Realm.

267
00:27:27,060 --> 00:27:29,440
All they want is freedom.

268
00:27:31,600 --> 00:27:35,020
Who is it that is so carefree?

269
00:27:35,020 --> 00:27:40,000
Zhi Xi's sister of the same blood, Yan Dan used half of her lotus heart

270
00:27:40,000 --> 00:27:42,040
