271
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:43,420
Yan Dan?

272
00:27:43,420 --> 00:27:47,900
That Yan Dan who staged an opera during the Jade Pool Festival?

273
00:27:47,900 --> 00:27:50,000
Then one who later jumped off the Bridge of Emptiness.

274
00:27:50,000 --> 00:27:55,420
Yan Dan, for whom you'd rather break your immortal spirit than forget?

275
00:27:57,280 --> 00:28:00,200
She loves you so much.

276
