with her this whole time.

279
00:28:08,920 --> 00:28:12,920
In the past, I wasn't willing to admit it.

280
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:17,640
But now... I just want to be true to myself.

281
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:19,760
Ying Yuan.

282
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:22,760
Ying Yuan.

283
00:28:22,760 --> 00:28:24,540
You're such a fool.

284
00:28:24,540 --> 00:28:28,080
Though the prohibitions in the Heavenly Realm have been eased slightly,

285
